israeli-jews-would-leave-israel-if-they-could-new-survey-finds/00000190-c202-d3e0-a5fd-ebb7ad1e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在 10 月 7 日的失败中装傻了。别相信他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-17/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-is-playing-dumb-on-his-october-7-failures-dont-believe-him/00000190-c1e5-d258-a3ff-e5ed94dd0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡竭尽全力避免政府对 10 月 7 日发生的情报、行动和领导失误进行正式调查，让他可以自由地编造自己的故事 — — 并逃避责任</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 19:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-17/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-is-playing-dumb-on-his-october-7-failures-dont-believe-him/00000190-c1e5-d258-a3ff-e5ed94dd0000</guid></item><item><title>美国禁止因杀害巴勒斯坦袭击者而被定罪的以色列士兵入境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-bans-entry-for-idf-soldier-convicted-of-killing-incapacitated-palestinian-assailant/00000190-c1d3-d13a-ad92-c9fb56490000</link><description>对前以色列国防军士兵埃洛尔·阿扎里亚及其家人的签证禁令可能是以色列首次因法外处决而被指定，开创了一个新的先例，可能会产生巨大的影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 18:37:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-bans-entry-for-idf-soldier-convicted-of-killing-incapacitated-palestinian-assailant/00000190-c1d3-d13a-ad92-c9fb56490000</guid></item><item><title>“诺亚，他在利用你”：家人准备抗议内塔尼亚胡的国会演讲，恳求获救人质不要加入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/families-prepare-to-protest-netanyahu-congress-speech-urging-rescued-hostage-not-to-join/00000190-c16a-d258-a3ff-e5eb96900000</link><description>人质亲属敦促诺亚·阿加马尼及其家人拒绝陪同总理在国会发表讲话的邀请。一位亲戚说，“我们会发现自己处于抗议你的荒谬境地，我们不希望这样”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 17:48:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/families-prepare-to-protest-netanyahu-congress-speech-urging-rescued-hostage-not-to-join/00000190-c16a-d258-a3ff-e5eb96900000</guid></item><item><titl