的民意调查各不相同，但明显的趋势是巴勒斯坦人之间的差距不断扩大，这取决于他们居住的地方和他们的经历。以下是哈马斯在加沙支持率下降的原因，以及为什么哈马斯的“抵抗”在约旦河西岸、巴勒斯坦侨民和亲巴勒斯坦盟友中仍被积极看待</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 11:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-popular-is-hamas-in-gaza-and-outside-of-it-after-nine-months-of-war/00000190-bfda-d211-a5da-ffdbea210000</guid></item><item><title>“这让我很惊讶，我不知道”：内塔尼亚胡对 10 月 7 日以色列军事基地发生的事情感到“惊讶”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-surprised-to-hear-what-happened-at-israeli-army-base-on-october-7/00000190-bfd0-d2f8-abdb-bff421df0000</link><description>第 12 频道新闻播出了内塔尼亚胡与在纳哈尔奥兹军事哨所被杀的以色列国防军女观察员家属会面的录音，显示总理不知道这些士兵没有携带武器，而且官员们探望了这些家庭</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:18:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-surprised-to-hear-what-happened-at-israeli-army-base-on-october-7/00000190-bfd0-d2f8-abdb-bff421df0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部发现六岁儿童尸体，母亲涉嫌谋杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/body-of-six-year-old-found-in-central-israel-mother-suspected-of-murder/00000190-c005-db81-a3f7-f29d11db0000</link><description>在尸体被发现之前，一名33岁的女子在荷兹利亚购物中心入口处用斧头袭击一名保安并轻伤了他，随后被捕。警方怀疑她是男孩的母亲，并且她患有精神疾病</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/body-of-six-year-old-found-in-central-israel-mother-suspected-of-murder/00000190-c005-db81-a3f7-f29d11db0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队向极端正统派男子发出数千份征兵通知，引发抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-issue-thousands-of-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-sparking-protests/00000190-bf3a-d458-a3d7-bfff171f0000</link><description>以色列军队预计将向正在犹太学院工作或已经退学的极端正统派男子发出约 6,000 份征兵通知。军队宣布这一消息后，大约 150 名来自极端极端正统教派的男子封锁了一条高速公路以示抗议</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 06:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-issue-thousands-of-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-sparking-protests/00000190-bf3a-d458-a3d7-bfff171f0000</guid></item><item><title>人权观察：至少五个巴勒斯坦团体在10月7日的袭击中犯有战争罪和反人类罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/human-rights-watch-at-least-five-palestinian-groups-committed-war-crimes-on-oct-7/00000190-bcfb-de8b-adfc-bdfbc1b30000</link><description>该组织的新报告反驳了哈马斯的说法，即其战斗人员被指示不要伤害儿童、妇女和老人，并指出对平民的杀害是有系统、有预谋和蓄意的</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/human-rights-watch-at-least-five-palestinian-groups-committed-war-crimes-on-oct-7/00000190-bcfb-de8b-adfc-bdfbc1b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军相信军事压力正在发挥作用，但表示哈马斯尚未被击败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-believes-military-pressure-is-paying-off-but-says-hamas-isnt-defeated-yet/00000190-bd16-d458-a3d7-bff7fb4b0000</link><description>以色列高级指挥官认为，现在与哈马斯达成协议的条件更好 ■ 与此同时，内塔尼亚胡及其政府的极右翼在谈判中没有表现出更大灵活性的迹象</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-believes-military-pressure-is-paying-off-but-says-hamas-isnt-defeated-yet/00000190-bd16-d458-a3d7-bff7fb4b0000</guid></item><item><title>尼基·黑利以以色列和伊朗为例，敦促共和党人团结起来支持特朗普</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/citing-israel-and-iran-nikki-haley-urges-republicans-to-unite-behind-trump/00000190-be6b-d2f8-abdb-be6fba2b0000</link><description>美国前驻联合国大使称赞特朗普的外交政策：“在以色列和哈马斯之间，唐纳德·特朗普清楚谁是我们的朋友，谁是我们的敌人”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:17:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/citing-israel-and-iran-nikki-haley-urges-republicans-to-unite-behind-trump/00000190-be6b-d2f8-abdb-be6fba2b0000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德主席敦促加沙达成协议，通知以色列部长内塔尼亚胡停战条件可能会阻止人质获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article-live/idf-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-in-latest-barrages-from-lebanon/00000190-be48-d3e0-a5fd-fffd18650000</link><description>以色列加强对加沙中部的打击； ■ 甘茨对内塔尼亚胡说：“你们推迟了拉法的攻势” ■ 真主党领袖威胁说，如果对平民的袭击加剧，他们将向以色列深处发动袭击 ■ 以色列国防军：部队在加沙地带北部遭到袭击，作为对周二针对斯德洛特的猛烈攻击的回应 ■ 以色列国防军发言人对阿拉伯电视台：哈马斯领导人&amp;#39; 固执正在阻止我们达成协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 01:38:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article-live/idf-dozens-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-in-latest-barrages-from-lebanon/00000190-be48-d3e0-a5fd-fffd18650000</guid></item></channel></rss>